    </div>
    <div class="cap-grid">
      <article class="cap-card" tabindex="0">
        <span class="cap-num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <div class="cap-body">
          <h3 class="cap-title">Concrete Contracting</h3>
          <p class="cap-desc">Concrete construction work delivered with attention to structural requirements and project scope. Contact the company directly to discuss your concrete project specifics.</p>
