          Discuss Your Project
          <svg aria-hidden="true" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </a>
      </article>
      <article class="cap-card" tabindex="0">
        <span class="cap-num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <div class="cap-body">
          <h3 class="cap-title">General Contracting</h3>
          <p class="cap-desc">Project-focused contractor support across construction work. Call to discuss your project type, location, timeline, and requirements to confirm fit and next steps.</p>
